description:
This is a 11 minute workout called 'Racing Strength' from the channel Peter Donohoe.
The workout falls under Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Progression Quest and The Meditative Grind vibe.
The The Progression Quest vibe means Methodical, incremental, long-term improvement. This is especially good for Anyone who loves tracking progress and leveling up. The The Meditative Grind vibe means Zone in, lock down, let repetition take over. This is especially good for Those who love a slow burn and rhythmic intensity..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Prepare to perform at your best with Peter in this workout designed to move freely, build strength, and handle the stress of life and racing. ...
